{"tid":1089922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"批《哈利波特》Kitty傘褻瀆神靈 波蘭神父焚書燒傘","createTime":"2019-04-03T06:13:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T07:18:53.000Z","uid":75969,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f26d3efc0f3ad3027a729c940334248d65a8495e","tid":1089922,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T06:13:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190402/large/1554192136_4e0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190402%2Flarge%2F1554192136_4e0d.jpg&h=d9aa6057&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n波蘭格但斯克（Gdansk）一個天主教福音派組織「SMS from Heaven」周日舉行彌撒後，在教堂焚燒一批書籍、物件，包括英國作家JK羅琳（J.K. Rowling）的小說《哈利波特》、印有「Hello Kitty」圖案的雨傘，聲稱它們褻瀆神靈。<br />\n<br />\n「SMS from Heaven」在其facebook專頁發文及上載照片，相中見到3位神父拿著一大籃書籍和物品，除了《哈利波特》外，還有以吸血鬼為背景的小說《吸血新世紀》（Twilight）、印有「Hello Kitty」圖案的雨傘、一個非洲風格的面具和印度教神像，丟到教堂外的一個火坑內燒毀，神父在火坑旁邊祈禱。<br />\n<br />\n帖文寫道「我們遵從神的話語」，又引述舊約聖經《申命記》（Deuteronomy）的經文。《申命記》勸導信徒毀滅神的敵人，包括「焚燒他們的偶像」。<br />\n <br />\n神父庫查斯基（Jan Kucharski）周一表示，他們要燒毀「與魔鬼和魔法有關」的物品，「除了書籍，還有辟邪物品及護身符」。<br />\n<br />\n他強調此舉與昔日納粹德軍等極權的文化審查行為不同，「我們知道甚麼會危害我們的信徒，所以要舉行這個活動，我甚至會稱之為狂熱。」<br />\n<br />\n有網民批評這種行為「落後」，「我相信只是開玩笑......認真的嗎？會有21世紀的人在病態的儀式中焚燒奇幻文學嗎？」，但亦有人留言支持，「消除一切不能取悅上帝的東西，看看你的生活會有甚麼變化」。<br />\n<br />\n《哈利波特》於1997年面世後，偶爾會受到宗教界或保守派抨擊，批評作品談及巫術。<br />\n中央社/英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190402/59440637\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190402%2F59440637&d=hsG%2BTWPyVhMSOc%2FhwZgu%2BvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=14a4af10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190402%2F59440637&h=5376e5c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190402/59440637</a>"},{"pid":"8b13db917c4c5ddf9398b4659a3cd40d6ae8b6d7","tid":1089922,"uid":162274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T06:22:24.000Z","msg":"但係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />關hello kitty咩事"},{"pid":"2a686a2431990e9d641355c7b5b054ee140e3969","tid":1089922,"uid":93062,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8b13db917c4c5ddf9398b4659a3cd40d6ae8b6d7","tid":1089922,"uid":162274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T06:22:24.000Z","msg":"但係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />關hello kitty咩事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T06:23:50.000Z","msg":"同神父件衫撞色<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e13d6088ca7fceeecbc145d4668c693067723ce","tid":1089922,"uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8b13db917c4c5ddf9398b4659a3cd40d6ae8b6d7","tid":1089922,"uid":162274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T06:22:24.000Z","msg":"但係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />關hello kitty咩事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T06:24:18.000Z","msg":"公仔識郁<br />\n仲唔係邪靈上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf2194d501880f758221e4efbb5cf6981b6630a","tid":1089922,"uid":107460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e13d6088ca7fceeecbc145d4668c693067723ce","tid":1089922,"uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8b13db917c4c5ddf9398b4659a3cd40d6ae8b6d7","tid":1089922,"uid":162274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T06:22:24.000Z","msg":"但係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />關hello kitty咩事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T06:24:18.000Z","msg":"公仔識郁<br />\n仲唔係邪靈上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T06:26:30.000Z","msg":"無口係邪靈象徵"},{"pid":"21b13b6ab8b50419bafe9cc3d10f5d962dc4741e","tid":1089922,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0